  {
    number: '01',
    title: 'Start with Your Context',
    description:
      'Use the city guides, rebate hub, and editorial resources to frame your lot conditions, style direction, and project priorities before you start comparing options.',
  },
  {
    number: '02',
    title: 'Compare Contractor Fits',
    description:
      'Browse contractor profiles organized by specialty and service area so you can see which approach feels right for your yard, budget, and timeline.',
  },
  {
    number: '03',
    title: 'Build a Smarter Brief',
    description:
      'Bring the ideas that fit into your contractor conversations. Your project brief, city notes, and rebate guidance help you arrive with a clearer scope.',
